---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<section id="mission" class="py-16 sm:py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-4">Focus Areas</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Articulatory dynamics and phonology are central to understanding speech production &mdash;
      with direct implications for education, clinical practice, and technology.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- Data Acquisition -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-brand-blue" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="2,16 6,10 10,20 14,8 18,24 22,12 26,18 30,16" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Articulatory Data Acquisition</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          Hardware and software systems for electromagnetic articulography (EMA),
          ultrasound tongue imaging, and optical motion capture (OptiTrack).
          End-to-end setup, calibration, and data collection pipelines.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Visualization & Feedback -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-brand-blue" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="2" y="4" width="28" height="24" rx="2" />
          <polyline points="6,22 12,14 16,18 22,10 26,14" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Speech Visualization & Feedback</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          Interactive tools for real-time articulatory feedback, acoustic analysis,
          and speech data exploration. Built for research labs, clinics, and classrooms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Software & Licensing -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow sm:col-span-2 sm:max-w-md sm:mx-auto md:col-span-1 md:max-w-none">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-brand-blue" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="10,8 4,16 10,24" />
          <polyline points="22,8 28,16 22,24" />
          <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="14" y2="26" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Software & Licensing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          Signal processing pipelines, deep learning models, and analysis toolkits
          for speech data. Available as licensed software or custom solutions.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
